ADA was started with the Scalper Brain and **immediately began trading**:

```
Starting ADA 2 Bot with Brain: Scalper Brain (Momentum Micro)
Bot loop started. Ticking every 5 seconds.
TAKE PROFIT HIT! P/L: 0.724% (target: +0.25%)
