## Next Steps for Improving the Scalper
The ScalperBrain was intentionally designed for iteration. Each entry/exit signal is a separate method:
- `_check_ema_crossover()` — upgrade with different EMA periods
- `_check_momentum_burst()` — tune the threshold
- `_check_rsi_bounce()` — try different RSI periods or thresholds
- `_check_ema_reversal()` — add trailing stop logic
- `_check_max_hold()` — make dynamic based on market conditions
- Add new signals by creating new `_check_*` methods
